title: [Icemule Defenses, East Wall]
description: The view to the northeast is dominated by the snow-capped mountains in the distance.  To the west, the neighborhood of Temple Burrow battles against the ice that flows from the glacier, across the north wall, and into the streets of Icemule Trace.

The view to the northeast reveals the darkened figures of mountains in the distance, their massive forms outlined in negative relief against the starlit sky.  To the west, the homes of Temple Burrow burn lights to keep the darkness at bay.
